headline: Better Energy Stock: EOG Resources vs. ConocoPhillips
summary: ConocoPhillips' long-cycle investments provide it with visible growth through the end of the decade.  EOG Resources expects to produce a lot of cash over the next few years.  ConocoPhillips (NYSE: COP) and EOG Resources (NYSE: EOG) are two of the country's largest independent exploration and production (E&P) companies.

headline: What Moved Markets This Week
summary: U.S. stocks fell on Friday, giving up all gains for the week, amid a sharp escalation between Israel and Iran. Read more about this week's major events on Wall Street.
